President Cyril Ramaphosa will lead government’s hosting of the second South Africa Investment Conference to be held at the Sandton Convention Centre in Johannesburg from 5 to 7 November 2019. The conference will be held under the theme Accelerating Growth by Building Partnerships. The annual conference is a key milestone in the country’s bold ambition to raise R1.2 trillion in new domestic and intentional investment over the next five years. Watch the conference on the stream below: 